This is a major release including many enhancements and bug fixes including:
  - Switch to a new PGP library which supports more encryption algorithms
  - Security enhancements
  - UI tweaks and bug fixes
  - Multi-language supports

Thanks to all contributors (@SimplyDanny, @ZortacDev, @merisbahti, @Moritz Kuntze, @davidjb) on these new features and enhancements. Also, thanks to our TestFlight users for very useful feedback.
